{"tid":2033551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"從「五大訴求」到「香港獨立」　國安惡法下港人的抗爭新面貌","createTime":"2020-05-24T17:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T18:00:38.000Z","uid":189,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90110ee09ad2a941c31dc756275518b53295c34a","tid":2033551,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T17:16:18.000Z","msg":"自從武漢肺炎疫情爆發以來，香港的反送中運動沉寂了一段時間。到近日北京主動出手制定「港版國安法」，香港今日再次出現萬人佔路、催淚煙四起的畫面。在經歷了接近一年的抗爭後，今日上街的示威者卻與以往有著微妙的差異。<br />\n<br />\n面對「國安法」的來臨，抗爭者的口號不再止於「五大訴求」，部分人更要求真正的「香港獨立」。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%89%B9%E5%AF%AB-%E5%BE%9E-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E5%88%B0-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%83%A1%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8B%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%96%B0%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25AF%25AB-%25E5%25BE%259E-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25B2%258C%2F&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=fbc46764\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25AF%25AB-%25E5%25BE%259E-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25B2%258C%2F&h=256e0336\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%89%B9%E5%AF%AB-%E5%BE%9E-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E5%88%B0-%E9